{"title":"克里姆林宫辞岁曲","authors":["池北偶"],"dates":[{"year":1977,"month":12,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"克里姆林宫辞岁曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池北偶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腊残岁尽更添愁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年往事难回首。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看国内，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皱眉头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粮食收成打折扣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了大炮缺黄油。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处借债受奚落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“发达社会”丢尽丑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“精神病院”患人满，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“全民国家”名声臭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太平日子何尝有？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屁股坐在火山口。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹牛白吹牛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遮羞难遮羞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扯住衣襟露出胳臂肘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望国外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眉头皱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“缓和”把戏看客稀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“裁军”假药难销售。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"特务间谍多落网，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雇佣卒子碰破头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红海之滨呼反霸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"非洲角上响怒吼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“天然盟友”现本相，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"超级大国栽跟斗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被轰的被轰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挨揍的挨揍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"画虎不成反类丧家狗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声长吁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几回短叹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少哀愁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别是一般滋味在心头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但愿从今交好运，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万事如意皆顺手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怕只怕无可奈何花落去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来年落花还依旧。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}